<p>New job? Gemma Collins added another string to her bow as she became a Bingo Caller during a drive-in bingo event at Events City, Manchester on Thursday night</p>

<p>Cutting a casual figure, Gemma donned a black bardot jumper dress, black leggings and matching sliders.</p>

